data.name: sqlCommand11.CommandText
data.value: SELECT dbo.tblAcordCadru.ID, dbo.tblAcordCadru.Denumire AS AcordCadru, dbo.tblAcordCadru.DataStart, dbo.tblAcordCadru.DataStop, dbo.tblAcordCadru.TipCentruID, dbo.tblPartener.Denumire AS Furnizor, dbo.tblProduse.Denumire AS Produs, (dbo.tblProduse.Pret + ISNULL( ( SELECT Valoare FROM dbo.tbxCotaTVA WHERE ID = dbo.tblProduse.CotaTVAID ), 0 ) * dbo.tblProduse.Pret / 100 ) AS Pret, dbo.tblAcordCadruDet.Cantitate AS CantitateTotala, dbo.tblAcordCadruDet.Valoare + dbo.tblAcordCadruDet.ValoareTVA AS Valoare, ISNULL( ( SELECT SUM(dbo.tblLotDet.Cantitate) FROM dbo.tblLotBase INNER JOIN dbo.tblLotDet ON tblLotDet.LotBaseID = dbo.tblLotBase.ID WHERE dbo.tblLotBase.AcordCadruID = dbo.tblAcordCadru.ID AND dbo.tblProduse.ID = dbo.tblLotDet.ProduseID ), 0 ) AS CantitateDistributa, Cantitate - ISNULL( ( SELECT SUM(dbo.tblLotDet.Cantitate) FROM dbo.tblLotBase INNER JOIN dbo.tblLotDet ON tblLotDet.LotBaseID = dbo.tblLotBase.ID WHERE dbo.tblLotBase.AcordCadruID = dbo.tblAcordCadru.ID AND dbo.tblProduse.ID = dbo.tblLotDet.ProduseID ), 0 ) AS Disponibil FROM dbo.tblAcordCadru INNER JOIN dbo.tblPartener ON dbo.tblAcordCadru.PartenerID = dbo.tblPartener.ID INNER JOIN dbo.tblAcordCadruDet ON dbo.tblAcordCadru.ID = dbo.tblAcordCadruDet.AcordCadruID INNER JOIN dbo.tblProduse ON dbo.tblAcordCadruDet.ProduseID = dbo.tblProduse.ID WHERE dbo.tblAcordCadru.DataStop IS NULL OR dbo.tblAcordCadru.DataStop >= @pDataLucru;
